{"tid":1909102,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"乾炒牛河溝辣椒醬","createTime":"2020-03-03T17:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T17:42:31.000Z","uid":350702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f93335af573d4f1769fdf1c7fabcc3dfa42549e","tid":1909102,"uid":350702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"平日我最鐘意食既就係乾炒牛河<br />\n一上枱就加半羹辣椒醬<br />\n果種味道直接令牛河昇華至另一個境界<br />\n牛肉既軟硬度<br />\n河粉既濕度<br />\n洋蔥銀芽既份量<br />\n師傅既手勢<br />\n各種各樣既材料炒埋一碟 可謂鑊氣逼人<br />\n如是者我食足十年<br />\n試過好多地方既乾炒牛河<br />\n每間茶記既味道都唔同<br />\n唯一不變既係溝辣椒醬之後既味道<br />\n但時至今日 我發現半羹辣椒醬已經滿足唔到我既味蕾<br />\n一羹 兩羹 三羹<br />\n開始有味道了<br />\n坐我側邊既阿叔望住我話<br />\n阿仔 咁後生就食咁重口味 日後你會發現你既味蕾會衰退 食咩都冇味<br />\n人呢 都係食健康d好<br />\n講完佢俾左羹蝦仁炒蛋我食<br />\n食完我望住個餐牌<br />\n原來有好多菜式我都未試過<br />\n人生苦短 鐘情牛河十年 <br />\n試下其他菜式拓寬味蕾何樂而不為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87c3eb3df22888f6e938bb4eed75b31aab15fdc","tid":1909102,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"0dc6d6be07443fe5cc2ee603ad564eb40923177c","tid":1909102,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"從來都未試過溝辣椒醬<br />\n有咩咁特別？<br />\n唔係幾鍾意辣椒陣味"},{"pid":"fea35521290109938a6f06e583d8ce93ea9d3b3a","tid":1909102,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"刮下脷苔"},{"pid":"6b30b685db819fdf10fd43c9b86267cfc04cf34a","tid":1909102,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dc6d6be07443fe5cc2ee603ad564eb40923177c","tid":1909102,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"從來都未試過溝辣椒醬<br />\n有咩咁特別？<br />\n唔係幾鍾意辣椒陣味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:31:25.000Z","msg":"醬"},{"pid":"51346d2ca0b00b52e76135205e9fc5b485ab003e","tid":1909102,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"轉gay垃圾post<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"23d435e12a337022e817b2df6c3ea2732b162497","tid":1909102,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51346d2ca0b00b52e76135205e9fc5b485ab003e","tid":1909102,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"轉gay垃圾post<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:34:29.000Z","msg":"同個牙叔體液交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841c960700f01e5538a1af46bc460e732264bbce","tid":1909102,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dc6d6be07443fe5cc2ee603ad564eb40923177c","tid":1909102,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"從來都未試過溝辣椒醬<br />\n有咩咁特別？<br />\n唔係幾鍾意辣椒陣味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"我會落是拉差辣椒醬，有蒜香味好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同牛肉都幾夾"}]}